With World Cancer Day taking place this past weekend, we wanted to highlight our imperatve partners in the industry - @bcppartners 

BCPP is the leading national organization of advocacy working towards eliminating chemicals and various other exposures linked to breast cancer. 

Princeton Tec has been partnered with @bcppartners since 1997 and donated over $50,000 in product donations to support their ever so important climbs, trips, and events. We believe BCPP, and all cancer research activism is integral to making our world a better, cancer-free place. From all of us at Princeton Tec, we encourage you to act and help eliminate unnecessary exposure to cancer with supporting @bcppartners 

To get involved with BCPP through events such as walks, hikes, and educational events, please visit: https://www.bcpp.org/get-involved/ 

OR 

To donate to the cause please visit: https://donate.bcpp.org/give/447262/#!/donation/checkout?c_src=whomeheader

To read more about BCPP and our partnership head over to our blog post linked below!

BLOG: https://princetontec.com/news/world-cancer-day-our-partnership-with-bcpp/

Princeton Tec is excited to introduce the UPGRADED Snap 450 RW, an even brighter take on our most versatile headlamp ever!

Snap is a unique headlamp that features a magnetic head unit, empowering it to become the ultimate multi-use light with 450 lumens and both red and white light.

The light can be worn as a traditional headlamp, used as a handheld flashlight, or fastened to any metal surface to brighten the area around you or your workspace!

While the Solo includes only the magnetic head unit and performance strap, the Kit includes a two way carabiner mount and clip for use as a lantern or attachment to your pack, as well as a handlebar attachment to mount to your bike or any similarly sized pole!  

Snap 450 RW is an all-in-one must have! 

Check it out using the link in our bio today! And keep checking back here for more on our NEW PRODUCT this week!
